ow\\n   150→\\n   151→```\\n   152→Agent produces code\\n   153→       │\\n   154→       ▼\\n   155→   Checkpoint\\n   156→       │\\n   157→       ▼\\n   158→  Run Proofs ──────► All Pass? ──► Auto-commit\\n   159→       │\\n   160→       ▼ Fail\\n   161→  Inject Feedback\\n   162→       │\\n   163→       ▼\\n   164→  Retry < Max? ──────► No ──► Escalate to Human\\n   165→       │\\n   166→       ▼ Yes\\n   167→  Agent Retries\\n   168→       │\\n   169→       └──────────────────────────────┘\\n   170→```\\n   171→\\n   172→### Configuration\\n   173→\\n   174→```json\\n   175→{\\n   176→  \\\"strategy_options\\\": {\\n   177→    \\\"validation\\\": {\\n   178→      \\\"auto_fix\\\": {\\n   179→        \\\"enabled\\\": true,\\n   180→        \\\"max_retries\\\": 3,\\n   181→        \\\"escalate_on_failure\\\": true\\n   182→      }\\n   183→    }\\n   184→  }\\n   185→}\\n   186→```\\n   187→\\n   188→## Phase 5: Autonomous Commit Mode (Proposed)\\n   189→\\n   190→Auto-commit when all proofs pass.\\n   191→\\n   192→### Goals\\n   193→\\n   194→- Zero human review for validated changes\\n   195→- Clean commit messages with proof summary\\n   196→- Full audit trail in metadata\\n   197→\\n   198→### New Strategy: `autonomous`\\n   199→\\n   200→```go\\n   201→type AutonomousStrategy struct {\\n   202→    base           *ManualCommitStrategy\\n   203→    validation     *ValidationRunner\\n   204→    maxRetries     int\\n   205→    autoCommit     bool\\n   206→    autoPush       bool\\n   207→}\\n   208→```\\n   209→\\n   210→### Commit Message Format\\n   211→\\n   212→```\\n   213→feat: implement user authentication\\n   214→\\n   215→Proofs passed:\\n   216→- tests: 142/142 ✓\\n   217→- coverage: 87% (≥80%) ✓\\n   218→- lint: 0 errors ✓\\n   219→- security: 0 vulnerabilities ✓\\n   220→\\n   221→Entire-Checkpoint: a3b2c4d5e6f7\\n   222→Entire-Autonomous: true\\n   223→```\\n   224→\\n   225→## Phase 6: Metrics & Observability (Proposed)\\n   226→\\n   227→Track va